author: bpendleton
msg: DERBY-4065: Provide documentation for XPLAIN style statistics processing
This follow-on change removes some XREF tag which attempted to construct
cross-manual reference linkages. Although these tags appeared to work
properly in the "HTML pages" format, they had a rather odd behavior (the
page would change but the TOC would not), and furthermore they did not
work at all in the PDF and HTML single-page formats.
Therefore, this change backs out the XREF tags which contained the
cross-manual references, and replaces them with simple textual references
to topic titles in the appropriate manual. That at least gives the user
a pointer about where to look for additional information.
